# Prefer the committed file `env.template` in this folder:
#   1. Copy `env.template` → `.env` (same directory as package.json)
#   2. Open `.env` and paste your RPC URL, mint, etc.
#   3. Run `scripts/sync-env.cmd` or `scripts/start-dev.cmd` (or `node scripts/sync-env.cjs` from repo root)
#
# `.env` is gitignored; `env.template` is safe to commit (no secrets).
